title: It's Already Set Up
itunes:title: It's Already Set Up
description:
When God laid out the plan for your life, He lined up everything you need to fulfill your destiny—every good break, person, solution and healing. If you’ll stay in faith and not let negative voices and situations talk you out of it, you’re going to come in to what God has already set up. You won’t have to go after it, it will come after you.To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
